1
00:01:10,919 --> 00:01:12,480
That fried noodle place by the entrance looks good.

2
00:01:12,639 --> 00:01:13,919
Let's watch the game when we get back tonight.

3
00:01:14,239 --> 00:01:14,800
Sure.

4
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:15,639
