5
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,760
Uncle Du, you're off work.

6
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:20,360
By the way, let's go home and have dinner together.

7
00:01:20,639 --> 00:01:21,239
Okay.

8
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,000
Let's go.

9
00:01:22,639 --> 00:01:24,120
Your bag is at home.

10
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:24,959
Okay.

11
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,639
The heart donor's family has been found.

12
00:01:28,239 --> 00:01:28,919
Coincidentally,

13
00:01:28,919 --> 00:01:30,199
