14
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,360
His name

15
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:32,279
is Du Jianlin.

16
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:34,120
It seems his son's heart

17
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:34,839
was transplanted into you.

18
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:37,040
But you must remember,

19
00:01:37,239 --> 00:01:38,839
