20
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:40,319
Otherwise, the consequences will be very serious.

21
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:41,720
Let me tell you,

22
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,239
for doctors,

23
00:01:43,559 --> 00:01:44,720
