27
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,199
You must be careful.

28
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,400
Make sure you don't let it slip.

29
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:24,960
President Gu

30
00:02:27,839 --> 00:02:28,759
Why are you here?

31
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,240
I was going to ask you that.

32
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,360
Why are you here?

33
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,679
I'm here to see Uncle Du.

34
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,160
He's from Tongzhou Factory.

35
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:36,600
You've met.

36
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:39,279
Isn't this

37
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:40,399
the one at the hospital that day,

38
00:02:40,399 --> 00:02:41,479
President Gu who scolded us?

39
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:44,440
What are you doing in such a remote place?

40
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,399
What happened at the hospital that day

41
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:47,759
