49
00:02:59,839 --> 00:03:00,679
I'm here looking for someone.

50
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,039
Looking for who?

51
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,720
I'm looking for the family that lives here.

52
00:03:04,279 --> 00:03:04,800
But

53
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:05,880
