54
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:06,839
What do you mean no one's home?

55
00:03:07,279 --> 00:03:07,919
I'm right here.

56
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,279
This is my house.

57
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:12,839
It's your house?

58
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,559
That's right.

59
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:17,000
Since President Gu is here,

60
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,520
