61
00:03:18,919 --> 00:03:19,919
Come inside and sit for a while.

62
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:20,880
Come on.

63
00:03:28,279 --> 00:03:29,479
President Gu, let's go.

64
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,839
Make yourselves at home.

65
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:33,880
You're guests here.

66
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:34,639
Come, come.

67
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:35,399
Uncle Du, you...

68
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:36,759
Please don't trouble yourself.

69
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,440
Is your

70
00:03:43,919 --> 00:03:44,720
wife not at home?

71
00:03:47,839 --> 00:03:48,880
She was in poor health

72
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,039
and passed away from illness long ago.

73
00:03:56,479 --> 00:03:57,160
Then

74
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,360
are your children not here with you?

75
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:01,039
President Gu.

76
00:04:01,559 --> 00:04:02,039
It's fine.

77
00:04:02,119 --> 00:04:02,720
Jiaqi,

78
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:04,559
it's okay.

79
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:06,880
Actually, as for me,

80
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:08,720
maybe my fate is just too tough.

81
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,960
Becoming family with me

82
00:04:11,559 --> 00:04:12,240
might

83
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:13,919
not be a good thing.

84
00:04:14,399 --> 00:04:16,279
I thought after marrying and having a son,

85
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:18,799
I could enjoy family happiness.

86
00:04:19,359 --> 00:04:20,279
I didn't expect

87
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,079
