88
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:25,359
After sending off my wife so early,

89
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:26,320
well,

90
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:29,000
I recently sent off my son too.

91
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,279
Otherwise,

92
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:31,720
Jiaqi

93
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:33,880
would have truly become family with me.

94
00:04:35,559 --> 00:04:37,679
