95
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,679
It seems you don't know.

96
00:04:40,119 --> 00:04:42,600
Jiaqi is my son's fiancée.

97
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:49,559
Your son

98
00:04:51,359 --> 00:04:52,279
is Du Zheng?

99
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,239
Yes.

100
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:54,920
The one at the factory that day

101
00:04:55,079 --> 00:04:56,119
who fought with you,

102
00:04:56,279 --> 00:04:57,359
that was my son.

103
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:59,200
Even though that kid

104
00:04:59,399 --> 00:05:00,799
was reckless and quick to fight,

105
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,600
to me,

106
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,359
he was the world's

107
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:06,119
one and only good son.

108
00:05:09,119 --> 00:05:10,640
After that kid left,

109
00:05:11,239 --> 00:05:12,519
I've aged a lot.

110
00:05:13,359 --> 00:05:14,519
My hair has turned quite gray.

111
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:16,799
But looking at you now,

112
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,799
you really do resemble my son a bit.

113
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:20,160
Look at you,

114
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:21,160
he was like that too.

115
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:22,839
Even at that age,

116
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,200
he was still a kid at heart,

117
00:05:24,359 --> 00:05:25,600
always chewing on a lollipop.

118
00:05:26,119 --> 00:05:26,839
Honestly.

119
00:05:34,239 --> 00:05:34,839
President Gu,

120
00:05:35,119 --> 00:05:35,799
what's wrong?

121
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:36,679
Are you okay?

122
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,000
I'm fine, I'm fine.

123
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:38,760
Jiaqi,

124
00:05:39,359 --> 00:05:40,519
help me call Qi Shuai.

125
00:05:41,119 --> 00:05:41,640
Okay.

126
00:05:43,679 --> 00:05:44,880
I never expected that the heart I received

127
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,600
would actually be Du Zheng's heart.

128
00:06:06,799 --> 00:06:07,640
Director Gu

129
00:06:08,239 --> 00:06:10,000
