133
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,920
Nelson is working quite hard.

134
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,040
He originally wanted to kick all these people out,

135
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:24,720
but now he has to win their hearts.

136
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,040
It's really quite amusing.

137
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:31,839
The people at the factory

138
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,320
won't be

139
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:34,359
