143
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:44,119
For him to rashly try and buy their loyalty

144
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,480
is almost impossible.

145
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,000
However,

146
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:50,359
Secretary Lin being entrusted by Director Gu

147
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:52,559
to visit Tongzhou Factory is the real problem.

148
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,359
Well,

149
00:06:54,359 --> 00:06:56,399
Director Gu does have conflicts with them,

150
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:58,519
but Secretary Lin's relationship with the workers

151
00:06:58,640 --> 00:06:59,799
is very close.

152
00:07:00,799 --> 00:07:01,519
Does Secretary Lin

153
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:03,320
visit Tongzhou Factory often?

154
00:07:03,679 --> 00:07:04,040
Yes.

155
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:06,239
According to reports from our people,

156
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:08,200
during her vacation, Secretary Lin

157
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:10,640
has been in contact with the factory's executives.

158
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:12,399
Her late fiance's

159
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,279
