160
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,920
I'm guessing

161
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:18,279
Secretary Lin is working on behalf of Director Gu

162
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,839
for his election as representative,

163
00:07:20,239 --> 00:07:21,160
running around to secure it.

164
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:27,640
No way.

165
00:07:28,959 --> 00:07:30,239
That's too much of a coincidence.

166
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:40,880
Yeah.

167
00:07:42,559 --> 00:07:43,679
Inside my body.

168
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:46,119
How could it be that person's heart?

169
00:07:47,079 --> 00:07:47,839
No.

170
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:50,559
You mean to say,

171
00:07:51,359 --> 00:07:53,799
the owner of the heart, that Du Zheng,

172
00:07:53,799 --> 00:07:54,799
Yes, yes, yes.

173
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,079
