174
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,959
Is that what you mean?

175
00:08:02,559 --> 00:08:03,600
I'm going crazy.

176
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,519
Oh my god.

177
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:07,440
This is too scary.

178
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:09,559
Look.

179
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,119
I've got goosebumps all over.

180
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,559
This feeling is so weird.

181
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,679
It's like...

182
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:20,799
It's like being possessed by something.

183
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,519
I feel like I'm not myself anymore.

184
00:08:24,119 --> 00:08:26,079
Ever since I had that heart surgery,

185
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,119
I've been changed

186
00:08:29,559 --> 00:08:30,720
by some kind of power.

187
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:33,599
No.

188
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,840
What did I tell you back then?

189
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,960
Don't look for the donor's information.

190
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,080
As long as you're healthy, that's all that matters.

191
00:08:39,599 --> 00:08:40,280
Now look at you.

192
00:08:40,479 --> 00:08:41,039
You found out,

193
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,320
and it just brings you more pain.

194
00:08:43,239 --> 00:08:44,159
I need to conduct

195
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,799
a comprehensive re-evaluation of Lin Jiaqi.

196
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:48,280
Evaluate what?

197
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:52,559
I'm starting to doubt the nature of these feelings.

198
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:55,200
Do I really like her?

199
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:57,280
Would you call this love?

200
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,960
I don't understand what you're saying.

201
00:09:00,719 --> 00:09:01,679
At first, I just thought

202
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:03,919
my own preferences had changed.

203
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,280
But now I feel

204
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:08,400
it's this heart playing tricks on me.

205
00:09:09,799 --> 00:09:10,679
This heart

206
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,679
is like a navigation system.

207
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,039
It's this heart,

208
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:17,479
it's this heart that chose Lin Jiaqi.

209
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:19,000
That's why my feelings for Lin Jiaqi

210
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,159
have changed.

211
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:23,520
If that's the case,

212
00:09:24,039 --> 00:09:25,840
then I wasn't the one who made this choice.

213
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,200
Right.

214
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,200
Right.

215
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,640
So how are you going to evaluate her?

216
00:09:35,359 --> 00:09:36,599
I need to think about this carefully.

217
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:38,159
You have to help me.

218
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,280
In the short term,

219
00:09:41,239 --> 00:09:44,000
I'll only maintain work-related contact with Lin Jiaqi.

220
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,359
I'll avoid all

221
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:46,640
private, one-on-one

222
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:47,479
contact.

223
00:09:48,359 --> 00:09:50,440
I need to analyze this rationally.

224
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,880
Is it really me who likes Lin Jiaqi,

225
00:09:55,719 --> 00:09:57,159
or is it the heart that likes her?

226
00:09:59,799 --> 00:10:03,239
How much I love you.

227
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:08,960
I love your bright smile.

228
00:10:09,479 --> 00:10:13,039
Moved by you countless times.

229
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:18,440
Like the sky after a storm.

230
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:23,880
Who are you?

231
00:10:25,039 --> 00:10:25,880
Who are you?

232
00:10:49,559 --> 00:10:50,039
Do you know

233
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:51,159
today is a very important day?

234
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:52,080
You don't have to tell me.

235
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:52,880
Where is Lin Jiaqi?

236
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:53,520
She

237
00:10:53,599 --> 00:10:54,840
went to Tongzhou Factory early this morning.

238
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:55,840
She left?

239
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:58,840
Weren't we supposed to go together?

240
00:10:59,440 --> 00:10:59,919
What's wrong?

241
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,520
You can just go with me.

242
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:04,640
Didn't she promise to go with me?

243
00:11:05,119 --> 00:11:06,239
How could she go back on her word?

244
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,159
Look at how pathetic you are.

245
00:11:10,559 --> 00:11:11,359
Let me tell you,

246
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,799
