247
00:11:13,119 --> 00:11:14,880
Put your romantic feelings aside for now.

248
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:15,359
Okay?

249
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:16,239
I don't have any.

250
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:18,280
You know in your heart whether you do or not.

251
00:11:19,559 --> 00:11:20,440
What about Secretary Lin?

252
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,880
She had to arrive early to set up the venue.

253
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:22,960
So she left early.

254
00:11:24,559 --> 00:11:25,640
Well, I didn't say anything.

255
00:11:26,599 --> 00:11:27,440
Today's task

256
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:28,880
must be completed perfectly.

257
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:29,840
Come on.

258
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:30,840
Before we leave,

259
00:11:31,479 --> 00:11:32,000
