268
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:04,119
Stop the car.

269
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:05,359
What's wrong?

270
00:12:05,359 --> 00:12:06,200
I said stop the car.

271
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:19,960
What's wrong?

272
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:27,880
Here.

273
00:12:29,880 --> 00:12:31,039
This place feels so familiar.

274
00:12:39,359 --> 00:12:40,000
What's wrong?

275
00:12:40,919 --> 00:12:41,840
Don't think about it for now.

276
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:43,960
Get in the car and rest.

277
00:12:45,679 --> 00:12:46,719
Come on, let's go.

278
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,119
Let's go. Get in the car and rest.

279
00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,039
Excuse me.

280
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:01,280
Could you tell me how to get to Tongzhou Factory?

281
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:06,159
You put the West Hall of Tongzhou Factory in the GPS.

282
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:07,760
We are at the East Hall here.

283
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:09,640
These two are not in the same place.

284
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:11,880
I see.

285
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,840
Just keep walking straight ahead now.

286
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:14,919
President Gu.

287
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,080
Are you okay?

288
00:13:16,559 --> 00:13:17,599
That place just now...

289
00:13:19,119 --> 00:13:20,599
Why did it look so familiar?

290
00:13:21,640 --> 00:13:23,520
The place where I lay bleeding in my dream...

291
00:13:24,640 --> 00:13:25,320
It was right there.

292
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:27,159
Don't scare me.

293
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:29,080
I... I've got goosebumps.

294
00:13:29,679 --> 00:13:30,039
Are you...

295
00:13:30,919 --> 00:13:32,280
Are you possessed or something?

296
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:33,559
I'm certain.

297
00:13:35,359 --> 00:13:36,359
It was right back there.

298
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:46,960
Was there a lot of traffic just now?

299
00:13:48,919 --> 00:13:49,760
It was pretty smooth.

300
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:50,919
Miss Lin.

301
00:13:51,039 --> 00:13:51,799
Uncle Feng.

302
00:13:52,359 --> 00:13:53,440
How come you arrived together?

303
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,239
They didn't know the way.

304
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,479
I brought them here.

305
00:13:57,039 --> 00:13:57,719
You know each other?

306
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,320
Yeah.

307
00:13:58,880 --> 00:14:00,520
Uncle Feng is the director's father.

308
00:14:00,919 --> 00:14:01,559
Director Feng?

309
00:14:01,559 --> 00:14:02,080
Yes.

310
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:03,280
I'll leave you to it.

311
00:14:03,640 --> 00:14:04,400
I need to get to work.

312
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:08,960
What's wrong?

313
00:14:10,239 --> 00:14:10,799
Nothing.

314
00:14:12,119 --> 00:14:13,359
Didn't we agree to come together?

315
00:14:13,719 --> 00:14:14,640
Why didn't you wait for me?

316
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:15,919
I had to set up the venue, didn't I?

317
00:14:17,479 --> 00:14:18,280
Excuse me.

318
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:19,840
Hello?

319
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:20,840
Uncle Du.

320
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,000
You still have the nerve to come.

321
00:14:32,719 --> 00:14:33,359
Uncle Du.

322
00:14:33,919 --> 00:14:34,679
What's going on?

323
00:14:36,359 --> 00:14:37,359
You two come over here and talk.

324
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:43,719
Take a look.

325
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:45,919
Distract Feimanzhi.

326
00:14:46,159 --> 00:14:48,239
Lure them into signing with Flair.

327
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:51,119
Push forward the layoffs at Tongzhou Factory.

328
00:14:53,919 --> 00:14:55,159
What on earth is going on?

329
00:14:55,799 --> 00:14:56,919
Right now, in the company,

330
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:58,840
everyone already has a copy.

331
00:14:59,239 --> 00:15:00,119
Lately,

332
00:15:00,119 --> 00:15:00,960
the evidence of President Gu's plan

333
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,280
to destroy this company

334
00:15:02,479 --> 00:15:04,440
is spreading wildly online and via flyers.

335
00:15:04,559 --> 00:15:05,520
Everyone knows about it now.

336
00:15:06,239 --> 00:15:07,960
Everyone heard that it was you, President Gu,

337
00:15:08,679 --> 00:15:10,039
who cut off Zhenyang Department Store

338
00:15:10,039 --> 00:15:11,840
and Crown Department Store's distribution channels.

339
00:15:12,799 --> 00:15:14,159
Then who spread all of this?

340
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:15,200
I don't know either.

341
00:15:15,559 --> 00:15:16,359
But Jiaqi,

342
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,599
I'm afraid canvassing for votes won't work this time.

343
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,640
Everyone heard that

344
00:15:20,919 --> 00:15:22,400
as a candidate for chairman,

345
00:15:22,679 --> 00:15:24,119
you actually did such a thing.

346
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,880
I really have no other way.

347
00:15:27,479 --> 00:15:29,200
But these are all things from the past.

348
00:15:29,799 --> 00:15:30,479
Right now, I am

349
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,159
truly and wholeheartedly

350
00:15:32,159 --> 00:15:33,239
doing this for the factory and the workers.

351
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:34,960
I know.

352
00:15:35,760 --> 00:15:37,559
Even though I promised you

353
00:15:37,799 --> 00:15:38,880
to help persuade everyone,

354
00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:40,359
but

355
00:15:40,679 --> 00:15:42,119
I don't have much confidence now.

356
00:15:42,479 --> 00:15:43,520
There are too many differing opinions.

357
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:44,599
People are saying all sorts of things.

358
00:15:45,119 --> 00:15:46,559
They won't just blindly listen to me.

359
00:15:47,559 --> 00:15:49,200
I really have no choice now.

360
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:51,200
Otherwise, you should just give up, Jiaqi.

361
00:15:51,359 --> 00:15:52,119
Uncle Du.

362
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:53,359
Let's try a little harder.

363
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:55,880
I'm sorry.

364
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:58,599
I hope you can understand my situation.

365
00:16:02,479 --> 00:16:03,719
I'll go talk to Uncle Du.

366
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:29,159
I can't believe

367
00:16:30,119 --> 00:16:32,039
I didn't fall at the hands of Gu Rongchen,

368
00:16:33,239 --> 00:16:35,320
but was held back by you,

369
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:36,880
Gu Rongchen's pawn.

370
00:16:37,719 --> 00:16:38,359
President Gu,

371
00:16:39,039 --> 00:16:41,200
you are a man of status and position.

372
00:16:42,280 --> 00:16:44,039
You should watch your language.

373
00:16:44,919 --> 00:16:45,599
Also,

374
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:47,159
don't talk about others.

375
00:16:47,679 --> 00:16:49,039
You're no better yourself.

376
00:16:49,919 --> 00:16:51,760
Aren't you also a pawn of Rosenmos?

377
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:52,559
What did you say?

378
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,359
I didn't mean anything else.

379
00:16:55,359 --> 00:16:56,559
I just wanted to remind you.

380
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,840
It's not me holding you back,

381
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:01,719
but your own past holding you back.

382
00:17:02,599 --> 00:17:03,400
I was just

383
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:05,439
telling everyone the truth.

384
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:09,359
There was no framing or rumor-mongering.

385
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:14,560
Feng Ziang, oh, Feng Ziang.

386
00:17:15,439 --> 00:17:16,920
You are really like Gu Rongchen.

387
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,439
For the position of chairman,

388
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:21,640
the way you both go all out...

389
00:17:22,719 --> 00:17:23,680
You're exactly the same.

390
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:26,319
I'm not just risking my life

391
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:28,040
for the chairman position.

392
00:17:29,359 --> 00:17:30,400
There's also Lin Jiaqi.

393
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:32,520
What are you trying to say?

394
00:17:32,959 --> 00:17:34,160
You're way too confident.

395
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:36,479
A pesky fly like you?

396
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:39,520
No man wants flies

397
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:40,959
buzzing around his woman.

398
00:17:41,439 --> 00:17:43,199
I don't want to see a pesky fly like you

399
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:45,000
buzzing around Lin Jiaqi either.

400
00:17:46,199 --> 00:17:47,000
Just wait and see.

401
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:49,400
I will never let that happen.

402
00:17:52,719 --> 00:17:53,599
Look at the time.

403
00:17:53,599 --> 00:17:54,680
Where did he go?

404
00:17:57,560 --> 00:17:58,680
He's still not answering his phone.

405
00:18:01,239 --> 00:18:01,839
President Gu.

406
00:18:03,599 --> 00:18:04,359
Where did you go?

407
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:05,680
Why didn't you answer your phone?

408
00:18:07,280 --> 00:18:08,319
I ran into Feng Ziang.

409
00:18:08,959 --> 00:18:09,640
What happened?

410
00:18:10,079 --> 00:18:10,839
What did you talk about?

411
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:12,959
The issue with the brochure,

412
00:18:13,959 --> 00:18:15,040
he's the one behind it.

413
00:18:15,719 --> 00:18:16,560
He did it?

414
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:19,959
I see.

415
00:18:20,359 --> 00:18:21,040
I'll go find him.

416
00:18:21,119 --> 00:18:21,719
Wait.

417
00:18:22,479 --> 00:18:23,319
You don't need to go.

418
00:18:24,119 --> 00:18:24,839
I told you,

419
00:18:25,079 --> 00:18:26,439
Feng Ziang is very dangerous.

420
00:18:26,800 --> 00:18:27,680
I'm begging you,

421
00:18:27,680 --> 00:18:29,319
don't have any contact with him from now on, okay?

422
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,520
Even though there's an unexpected rival now,

423
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:35,599
whatever move he makes,

424
00:18:36,319 --> 00:18:37,239
we'll counter every move.

425
00:18:37,800 --> 00:18:38,439
That's all.

426
00:18:39,199 --> 00:18:39,839
Jiaqi.

427
00:18:41,239 --> 00:18:41,719
Yaoyao.

428
00:18:43,560 --> 00:18:44,359
I have something to tell you.

429
00:18:44,439 --> 00:18:45,359
Come with me for a second.

430
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:46,680
Okay.

431
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:49,640
I'll be right back.

432
00:18:52,719 --> 00:18:53,680
She glared at me.

433
00:19:10,439 --> 00:19:11,040
I know.

434
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:12,439
It's because of that...

435
00:19:12,959 --> 00:19:15,199
Because of Jiaqi's boyfriend's death.

436
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:18,119
That Du Zheng,

437
00:19:18,439 --> 00:19:20,760
he died in a hit-and-run, right?

438
00:19:21,959 --> 00:19:22,839
And I heard

439
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:23,959
that until now,

440
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:25,599
the hit-and-run suspect hasn't been found.

441
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:27,640
They haven't caught him yet?

442
00:19:28,520 --> 00:19:30,000
That's what my source says.

443
00:19:31,119 --> 00:19:32,800
Is your source reliable?

444
00:19:50,239 --> 00:19:50,800
By the way,

445
00:19:51,719 --> 00:19:52,439
that Du Zheng...

446
00:19:53,319 --> 00:19:54,839
Was he on the road near the factory

447
00:19:54,839 --> 00:19:55,439
when the accident happened?

448
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:56,880
How did you know?

449
00:19:57,119 --> 00:19:57,719
Did I tell you that?

450
00:19:58,199 --> 00:19:59,040
So it is true.

451
00:19:59,719 --> 00:20:00,479
I heard

452
00:20:00,479 --> 00:20:01,199
it was near

453
00:20:01,520 --> 00:20:02,760
his father's house,

454
00:20:03,040 --> 00:20:03,920
which is also near

455
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:04,800
Tongzhou Factory, right?

456
00:20:07,079 --> 00:20:07,680
Qi Shuai,

457
00:20:08,199 --> 00:20:09,079
go and check for me

458
00:20:09,599 --> 00:20:10,760
if the scene of Du Zheng's accident

459
00:20:11,199 --> 00:20:12,800
is the road where we got lost last time.

460
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:14,439
Also,

461
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:16,199
regarding the progress of this investigation,

462
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:17,439
keep me updated at all times.

463
00:20:18,199 --> 00:20:18,800
Okay.

464
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:21,040
But why are we looking into this?

465
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:22,920
I think

466
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:24,560
I might know

467
00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:26,199
the reason for my chronic nightmares.

468
00:20:32,959 --> 00:20:33,719
What did you say?

469
00:20:34,520 --> 00:20:36,040
This case wasn't a hit-and-run,

470
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:37,479
but a murder?

471
00:20:38,560 --> 00:20:39,400
So,

472
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:41,000
Du Zheng was actually

473
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,319
secretly investigating substandard materials,

474
00:20:42,959 --> 00:20:44,280
and because he found an important clue,

475
00:20:44,280 --> 00:20:45,520
he was silenced, right?

476
00:20:46,079 --> 00:20:47,119
Don't panic just yet, you two.

477
00:20:47,800 --> 00:20:49,439
Right now, we only have reason to suspect

478
00:20:50,040 --> 00:20:51,199
that it wasn't a hit-and-run.

479
00:20:51,920 --> 00:20:52,520
Right.

480
00:20:52,959 --> 00:20:53,520
Because

481
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:55,079
before Tan Feng had his accident,

482
00:20:55,079 --> 00:20:55,880
that's what he said.

483
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:56,959
In other words,

484
00:20:57,560 --> 00:20:58,880
as soon as Tan Feng wakes up,

485
00:20:59,280 --> 00:21:00,640
we can get his testimony.

486
00:21:01,439 --> 00:21:02,800
Then all the questions regarding this case

487
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:03,760
can be solved immediately.

488
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,079
So, Uncle Du,

489
00:21:05,319 --> 00:21:06,000
Jiaqi,

490
00:21:06,359 --> 00:21:07,599
please don't be sad for now.

491
00:21:07,959 --> 00:21:08,920
Let's wait a little longer, okay?
